育自由行。<br />\n7. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n8. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n9. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n10. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n11. Tag或吹你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加，如果你咁都做唔到，講咩野好忟好惱無野可做。<br />\n只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。"},{"pid":"78f98c900be182e8b41276fb3a6e1965fac670d3","tid":1530772,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a7cffe61e503727b5bac62204bab5c263dc152","tid":1530772,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"咁仲入唔入去揸春袋？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"所以先想問<br />\n<br />\n春袋定美領"},{"pid":"4e9a0df0280573447b8f94c36f0e8f67ebce3692","tid":1530772,"uid":46910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"推呀 9月冇時間表呀"},{"pid":"69bd788703a5e494da95e1ba7dd7618c9b3c1d82","tid":1530772,"uid":39221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78f98c900be182e8b41276fb3a6e1965fac670d3","tid":1530772,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"16a7cffe61e503727b5bac62204bab5c263dc152","tid":1530772,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:25:10.000Z","msg":"咁仲入唔入去揸春袋？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"所以先想問<br />\n<br />\n春袋定美領"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:28:27.000Z","msg":"美領<br />\n美國國會開會呀"},{"pid":"6107db938685ddd342b12cbdfdef6db2596b6dc5","tid":1530772,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"又話機場月"},{"pid":"f643ffd7cc6bae9708c4a720542050128e66dc04","tid":1530772,"uid":14026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6107db938685ddd342b12cbdfdef6db2596b6dc5","tid":1530772,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:29:18.000Z","msg":"又話機場月"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"所以先要傾<br />\n唔傾文宣點出？"},{"pid":"5136b54418b098ddb5bb480de921a21f112a9c35","tid":1530772,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f643ffd7